      <category>Zagreb</category>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2019 09:56:29 GMT</pubDate>
      <guid>https://www.jutarnji.hr/vijesti/zagreb/video-cistoca-napokon-uklonila-glomazni-otpad-iz-centra-zagreba-nepoznati-ljudi-kombijima-nocu-istovarivali-smece-jednog-muskarca-snimili-su-stanari/9252305/</guid>
