      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2019 06:03:00 GMT</pubDate>
      <guid>https://www.jutarnji.hr/vijesti/top/nauticka-patrola/bivsi-pomorac-33-godine-radi-na-gatovima-dubrovacke-marine-kako-je-roko-belemecic-uspio-pomiriti-ljubav-prema-pucini-valovima-i-supruzi-eleni/9250862/</guid>
